   Gibernau, Marc, Univ Toulouse 3, UMR 5174, Lab Evolut \& Diversite Biol, F-31062 Toulouse 9, France.
   Chouteau, Mathieu; Barabe, Denis, Univ Montreal, Inst Rech Biol Vegetale, Montreal, PQ H1X 2B2, Canada.},
ISSN = {0024-4074},
Keywords = {bee; beetle; climatic conditions; fly pollination; life cycle; pollen to
