   Do Amaral Navarro, Daniela Maria, Univ Fed Pernambuco, Dept Fundamental Chem, Recife, PE, Brazil.
   Maia, Artur Dalia, Univ Fed Pernambuco, Grad Program Anim Biol, Recife, PE, Brazil.
   Maia, Artur Dalia, Univ Fed Paraiba, Grad Program Biol Sci, Joao Pessoa, Paraiba, Brazil.},
