   Sugiura, S (Corresponding Author), Kobe Univ, Grad Sch Agr Sci, 1-1 Rokkodai,Nada Ku, Kobe, Hyogo 6578501, Japan.
   Suetsugu, Kenji; Nishigaki, Hiroki, Kobe Univ, Grad Sch Sci, Dept Biol, Kobe, Hyogo, Japan.
