   Kakishima, Satoshi, Natl Museum Nat \& Sci, Dept Bot, Tsukuba, Ibaraki, Japan.
   Sueyoshi, Masahiro, Forest Res \& Management Org, Forestry \& Forest Prod Res Inst, Ctr Biodivers \& Climate Change, Tsukuba, Ibaraki, Japan.
